<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="itself-pron">itself <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪt'self/    美 /ɪt'self/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>它自己；它本身：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The chance will not find you itself.
机会不会自己送上门。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>History repeats itself.
历史重演。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="by-itself">by itself</h3>
<p>1.<strong>单独地；独立地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The tree stands by itself in the garden. 
那棵树孤零零地立在花园中。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Surprisingly, Susan's beautiful hair reached below her knees and made <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (it) almost an overcoat for her.
  （2011 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. itself  </p></div>